SELECT 
  c.person_first_name, 
  c.person_last_name, 
  o.order_date, 
  o.total_amount, 
  p.product_name, 
  SUM(oi.quantity * oi.price_per_unit) AS total_order_value
FROM 
  customerinfo c
  JOIN orders o ON c.person_customer_id = o.person_customer_id
  JOIN order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
  JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.unique_product_identifier
WHERE 
  o.order_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
  AND p.product_category_primary = 'Electronics'
  AND oi.quantity > 1
GROUP BY 
  c.person_first_name, 
  c.person_last_name, 
  o.order_date, 
  p.product_name
ORDER BY 
  total_order_value DESC;
